    schema:description """IUCN protected area management category: National Park

Authority: Queensland Department of Environment and Science

Governance: Joint - Jointly managed protected areas where several social actors from different governance types share decision-making authority, responsibility and accountability. Joint management arrangements are recognised by a management board, agreement (e.g. ILUA) or other formal arrangement.""" ;
